definition: walk a hundred steps after each meal and you will live a long life (proverb)
pinyin: fan4 hou4 bai3 bu4 zou3 , huo2 dao4 jiu3 shi2 jiu3
containing_words.word: 饭后百步走，活到九十九

sentences.english: “We have done this every June for nineteen years, ” he said.
sentences.chinese: 每年逢六月，我们这样做，现已经有十九年了。

sentences.english: The words of the equivalent of 19 AnLun times of enlightenment.
sentences.chinese: 经论字数相当于十九部《菩提道次广论》。

sentences.english: The whole trip took him 19 years before he returned to Chang'an.
sentences.chinese: 花了整整十九年的时间，最后回到了长安。

sentences.english: Public celebration of the Eucharist in the Roman Catholic Church and some Protestant churches.
sentences.chinese: 十九世纪从罗马天主教分离出来的天主教派。

sentences.english: If a man owns a hundred sheep, and one of them wanders away, will he not leave the ninety-nine on the hills and go to look for the one that wandered off?
sentences.chinese: 他岂不撇下这九十九只，往山里去找那只迷路的羊么。

sentences.english: He was twenty-five years old when he became king, and he reigned in Jerusalem twenty-nine years.
sentences.chinese: 他登基的时候年二十五岁，在耶路撒冷作王二十九年。

sentences.english: 99 percent of lawyers give the rest a bad name.
sentences.chinese: 百分之九十九的律师是毁坏律师界名声的大老鼠。

sentences.english: It's built in the nineteenth century.
sentences.chinese: 埃菲尔铁塔始建于十九世纪。

sentences.english: During the XIX century, the English owned the tea marked in China.
sentences.chinese: 在十九世纪，英国控制着中国的茶叶市场。

sentences.english: Meet Grady, a twenty-nine year old construction worker.
sentences.chinese: 米特格雷迪，一个二十九岁的建筑工人。

sentences.english: It had been nineteen years since Yellow Emperor unified the country.
sentences.chinese: 黄帝一统天下已经十九年了。

sentences.english: They were called up at the age of nineteen.
sentences.chinese: 他们十九岁时被征召入伍。

sentences.english: In our history, staging refers to the era before the mid-nineteenth century.
sentences.chinese: 在我国历史分期上泛指十九世纪中叶以前的时代。

sentences.english: Dancing and laughing along the beach came the twenty-ninth bather.
sentences.chinese: 跳著，笑著，沿著海滩，第二十九个沐浴者来了。

sentences.english: He was born at nine- nineteen at night. I will never forget that night.
sentences.chinese: 他在晚九点十九分出生我永远也忘不了那个晚上。

sentences.english: Article 169. An independent director may submit his resignation before the expiration of his term.
sentences.chinese: 第一百六十九条独立董事在任期届满钱可以提出辞职。
